    <official-title>To amend <external-xref legal-doc="usc-chapter" parsable-cite="usc-chapter/5/77">chapter 77</external-xref> of title 5, United States Code, to clarify certain due process rights of Federal employees serving in sensitive positions, and for other purposes.</official-title>
